<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang='en'>
  <head>
  <title> Return Picked Up </title>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px;">
    <h1 style="color: #2E86C1; text-align: center;">Return Picked Up</h1>
    <p>
      Dear Customer,
    </p>
    <p>The product you returned has been picked up by our courier partner.</p>
    <p>Once it reaches our warehouse, we will do a quality check of the product. If the quality check is successful, we will initiate a refund.</p> 
    <ul>
      <li>Return Details:</li>
      <% return_detail = @order_item.return_exchange_requests&.last %>
      <% if return_detail.present? %>
      <ul>
        <li>Order No: <%= @order.order_number %></li>
        <li>Product: <%= @order_item&.catalogue&.product_title %></li>
        <li>Quantity: <%= @order_item&.quantity %></li>
        <li>Price: <%= @order_item&.price %></li>
        <li>Request type: <%= return_detail&.request_type %></li>
        <li>Request Reason: <%= return_detail&.request_reason %></li>
        <li>Description: <%= return_detail&.description %></li>
      </ul>
      <% end %>
    </ul>
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>The Byezzy Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
